Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should at least know the name\Nof the man who killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:30.65,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,200)\pos(362,351)}A Man Without a Name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how could this have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was such a wonderful man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He put his life on the line for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to find Inspector Lunge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This letter the Inspector asked Mr. Grimmer to keep...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Inspector Lunge found it at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've been watching you all this time."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To eat up every bit of you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But instead, everything about you has devoured me."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When I was on the verge of falling\Napart, how did I look to you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That which you gave me as I was falling apart..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You left me with such beautiful jewels."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The twins, who are like eternal life itself."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The greatest sin is to take away a person's name."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Reclaim your name."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I return your name to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your name is... Anna."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm filled with sorrow now."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Filled with sorrow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Filled with sorrow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Filled with sorrow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Filled with sorrow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Filled with sorrow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wrote this, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in love with the mother of the twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My way of thinking changed completely in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed everyone who knew about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone who knew about the twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone who knew about the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die from that wound if you don't treat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my questions if you want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you gone this far to obey Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you related to Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How far you have fallen, Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brilliant agent of the BKA...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is here in this country town, all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a sightseeing vacation without even his police badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you looked too deeply into\Na senate member's scandal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were hung out to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you exist only to chase after Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife is living with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandson thinks that man is his grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just started to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept calling that man, "Grandpa! Grandpa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandson is growing up to be a cute little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have sunk pretty low.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old Inspector Lunge wasn't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I'm related to Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized my first memory while \N working after escaping the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, Johan appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped me recall one of my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was his real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His own name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me he was in an orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he told me once...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that even though he had forgotten everything\Nelse, he remembered his friend's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He forgot his own name, but remembered his friend's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that person liked to draw, and he loved bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't like to kill bugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he would set them free from their cages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think his name was Adolf Reinhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he loved the cocoa they were given once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan came to me and offered me a mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I looked forward to each\Nweek while I was at the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved that warm cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if the rain washed everything clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in actuality, the complete opposite happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was blown out of proportion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was raining like this on that day, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.90,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, Mr. Liebert, the East German foreign trade adviser...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:59.49,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,who emigrated to the West from the East...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:03.70,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,appeared before the media with his wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.58,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lieberts showed no sign of fatigue...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:09.33,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,and appeared happy, standing with their two children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you also an emigrant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, from Czechoslovakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you knew these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a glance will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just their sleeping faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tragedy happened that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.84,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Survivor confirmed, one young girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.18,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,A man and a woman are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.43,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy is severely wounded, but he has a pulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.06,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.68,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood,pressure, 72/50!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:08.48,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse, 137!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.44,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,So the bullet entered in the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.32,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any idea what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew everything, but I ran away from it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped thinking about everything, and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to draw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture of the ideal twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those children enveloped in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no matter how many times I tried,\NI just couldn't draw something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lunge is at Hotel Bergbach, just ahead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows where they're aiming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I created a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I revived that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't kill you, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no strength in my right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was shot by Dr. Tenma in the library in Munich, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been easy to kill him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Dr. Tenma is someone who will remain standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will be the last man standing, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will die in solitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and without a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Johan's calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma was allowed to see\Nthe landscape that Johan saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see that landscape, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lunge, you won't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is part of Johan's calculation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calculation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such calculations can't be processed\Nby the computer in my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's watching from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like watching a line of ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's search inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was where Tenma was headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl from the drawings...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, the girl from the drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were lots of drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look just like the girl in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was with a boy with the same face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were drawings of twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you see those drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l-lt was in the vampire's mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right on top of the hill to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, has anyone seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone seen my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Wim go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A devil came to this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that no one is here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan was here not too long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is what you're saying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all attempts at drawing you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're all unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all smiling happily in the drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who drew these was Franz Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Johan felt when he saw these drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:18:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saw a scary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A very, very scary thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Rose Mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone drank the wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone started to suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all collapsed on top of each other before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two had to live on your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please live on your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until just now, in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was crying, just like that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that rainy night...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had forgiven him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this wouldn't have continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This many people wouldn't have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Johan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To end everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.95,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:44.38,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:44.38,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:47.34,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:23:01.02,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:23:01.02,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:25.88,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:34.30,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.76,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
